ext_description.note:
If the month_component is 'April', 'June', 'August', or 'November' the day_component will be between 1 and 30; 
when the month_component is 'February' and the 

is a leap year the day_component will be between 1 and 29; 
if the month_component is 'February' and the 

is not a leap year the day_component will be between 1 and 28. 
Otherwise, the day_component will be between 1 and 31.
